name: Linsey Levendall
bio: South African born artist, illustrator and conceptual designer living in rural Canada.

social_posts.post_text: Pulled an all nighter at the studio. One of two artworks I was painting in the early hours of the morning.
Oil painting for a dear friend whom I greatly appreciate.
It’s my 40th. Thank you to those who got me through a rough last year!
Been on a yellow trip for a bit now and still not sick of it. Been soothing.
2 years without you. Miss you so much Dad!
Design I made for a pop up event on Sunday. Came up with the rough design at a local coffee shop #airmaxday #airmaxmonth #linseylevendallart
Live painting I made last night for a charity I support in my community. Heart is full.

Declaration of Love for my kids during their birthday month. Grateful for everyone who made this possible by helping me and allowing me to spread light through my art. Located in my lil Saskatchewan town of Melfort, behind TJ’s pizza. Thank you Tara and Lloyd!
“Love over Everything” - For Talulah Nova & Takoda Anakin.
South African born artist, illustrator and conceptual designer living in rural Canada.
